name: Gigi Hadid Embedding
description:
Jelena Noura "Gigi" Hadid (born April 23, 1995) is an American model and television personality. In November 2014, she made her debut in the Top 50 Models ranking at Models.com. In 2016, she was named International Model of the Year by the British Fashion Council. Over the span of four years, she has made 35 appearances on international Vogue magazine covers.

If you like my work and you feel like it, you can invite me to a Ko-fi!
